 - Abstract base class implementing ConsumerPartitionAssignor interface. Provides common functionality including partition collection, rack-aware assignment logic, and member information management. All assignor implementations extend from this class either directly or through AbstractStickyAssignor.\n\n6. **AbstractStickyAssignor** (clients/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/consumer/internals/AbstractStickyAssignor.java) - Intermediate abstract base class extending AbstractPartitionAssignor. Contains shared sticky assignment implementation used by both StickyAssignor and CooperativeStickyAssignor. Implements rack-aware assignment with partition movement tracking, supporting both eager and cooperative rebalancing protocols."
